To create a script that activates a UI GameObject and fades it out over time, you will need to work with a `CanvasGroup` component that allows fading by adjusting its `alpha` property. If the UI GameObject you are fading does not already have a `CanvasGroup`, you will need to add it using the Unity Editor or programmatically.

